Zigbee Module
-------------

|Product| supports an onboard Zigbee module. The Zigbee controller is TI CC2531, and the Raspberry Pi forum supports it. |br| |br|
For |productP|, there is a connector on the backside of the case that you can use to connect the external Zigbee antenna, as described in the figure below.

.. figure:: /Media/Pi/A72/Others/ZigBee_Con.jpeg
   :align: center
   :figclass: align-center

   *Zigbee controller*


.. rst-class:: text-center

   |zigbee_img|

   *Zigbee Antenna*


.. attention::

    The product does not come with the Zigbee module by default.